#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Introduction</title>"
msgstr "<title>Uvod</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: introduction.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Introduction</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Uvod</primary>"

#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Package description"
msgstr "Opis paketa"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader; is a simple, easy, powerful, twin-panel file manager (commander-"
"style) for &plasma; and other *nix desktops, similar to "
"<application>Midnight Commander</application> or <trademark class=\"copyright"
"\">Total Commander</trademark>. It provides all the file management features "
"you could possibly want."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; je preprost, enostaven, zmogljiv upravljalnik datotek z dvema "
"ploščama (v slogu ukaznika) za &plasma; in druga namizja *nix, podobna "
"<application>Midnight Commander</application> ali <trademark class="
"\"copyright\">Total Commander</trademark>. Zagotavlja vse funkcije za "
"upravljanje datotek, ki bi jih morda želeli."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Krusader also includes extensive archive handling, mounted file system "
"support, &FTP;, advanced search module, viewer/editor, folder "
"synchronization, file content comparisons, powerful batch renaming and much, "
"much more. &krusader; supports archive formats: ace, arj, bzip2, deb, gzip, "
"iso, lha, rar, rpm, tar, zip and 7-zip and handles other KIO Slaves such as "
"smb:// or fish://."
msgstr ""
"Krusader vključuje tudi obsežno upravljanje arhivov, podporo za nameščen "
"datotečni sistem, &FTP;, napredni iskalni modul, pregledovalnik/urejevalnik, "
"sinhronizacijo map, primerjave vsebine datotek, zmogljivo paketno "
"preimenovanje in še veliko, veliko več. &krusader; podpira formate arhivov: "
"ace, arj, bzip2, deb, gzip, iso, lha, rar, rpm, tar, zip in 7-zip ter "
"obravnava druge sužnje KIO, kot sta smb:// ali fish://."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader; is almost completely customizable and therefore very user-"
"friendly."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; je skoraj popolnoma prilagodljiv in zato uporabniku zelo prijazen."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "Try &krusader;."
msgstr "Poskusite &krusader;."

#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "&krusader; screenshot"
msgstr "&krusader; posnetek zaslona"

#. Tag: phrase
#: introduction.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "&krusader; screen shot"
msgstr "&krusader; posnetek zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More <ulink url=\"https://krusader.org/\">&krusader; Screenshots</ulink> can "
"be viewed on our website."
msgstr ""
"Več <ulink url=\"https://krusader.org/\">&krusader; Posnetke zaslona</ulink> "
"si lahko ogledate na naši spletni strani."

#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "Welcome to &krusader;!"
msgstr "Dobrodošli v &krusader;!"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Our aim is to give you a simple, intuitive tool that easily handles the most "
"important tasks you perform on your computer each and every day: manage and "
"process your files the way you want."
msgstr ""
"Naš cilj je, da vam ponudimo preprosto, intuitivno orodje, ki enostavno "
"obravnava najpomembnejša opravila, ki jih vsak dan opravljate na vašem "
"računalniku: upravljajte in obdelujte svoje datoteke, kot želite."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether you are a &Linux; expert or a novice, &krusader; makes routine file "
"management tasks quick and accurate, allowing you to focus on the big "
"picture, not command line syntax. This is especially helpful if you are new "
"to xxNIX operating systems. To do just that, &krusader; uses a good-looking "
"&GUI; and supports drag and drop as well as &MIME; types, making it easy to "
"use."
msgstr ""
"Ne glede na to, ali ste &Linux; strokovnjak ali novinec, &krusader; naredi "
"rutinska opravila upravljanja datotek hitra in natančna, kar vam omogoča, da "
"se osredotočite na veliko sliko, ne na sintakso ukazne vrstice. To je še "
"posebej koristno, če ste novi v operacijskih sistemih xxNIX. Če želite "
"narediti prav to, &krusader; uporablja lep &GUI; in podpira povleci in "
"spusti ter &MIME; vrste, zaradi česar je uporaba enostavna."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader; has many useful features. It is fast, and handles <link linkend="
"\"archives\">archives</link> transparently. In addition, &krusader; "
"streamlines many complex file management tasks, reducing fatigue, errors, "
"and distraction. Basically, &krusader; provides all the helpful features you "
"have come to expect from other quality file management tools like "
"<application>Midnight Commander</application> and <trademark class="
"\"copyright\">Total Commander</trademark>. &krusader; is designed to "
"integrate seamlessly with the &plasma;, the desktop of choice for many "
"programmers, network engineers, and other power users of &Linux;. With "
"&krusader; even novice users can quickly access the power, convenience, and "
"feature rich capabilities of the &plasma;. &krusader; is a free open-source "
"project, and it is released under the <link linkend=\"credits\">&GNU; "
"General Public License (GPL)</link>, although the developers still retain "
"the copyright for the project and its name, and manage the project's "
"continuing evolution."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; ima veliko uporabnih funkcij. Je hiter in pregledno obravnava "
"<link linkend=\"archives\">arhive</link>. Poleg tega &krusader; poenostavi "
"številne zapletene naloge upravljanja datotek, zmanjša utrujenost, napake in "
"motnje. V bistvu &krusader; ponuja vse koristne funkcije, ki ste jih "
"pričakovali od drugih kakovostnih orodij za upravljanje datotek, kot sta "
"<application>Midnight Commander</application> in <trademark class=\"copyright"
"\">Total Commander</trademark>. &krusader; je zasnovan za brezhibno "
"integracijo s &plasma;, namizjem po izbiri mnogih programerjev, omrežnih "
"inženirjev in drugih naprednih uporabnikov &Linux;a. Z &krusader; tudi novi "
"uporabniki lahko hitro dostopajo do moči, udobja in bogatih funkcij "
"&plasma;. &krusader; je brezplačen odprtokodni projekt in je izdan pod <link "
"linkend=\"credits\">&GNU; Splošna javna licenca (GPL)</link>, čeprav "
"razvijalci še vedno obdržijo avtorske pravice za projekt in njegovo ime ter "
"upravljajo nadaljnji razvoj projekta."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &krusader; Project mission is to create an <quote>all-in-one</quote> "
"file manager, which will do all the ordinary things you would expect of it, "
"and more. Since the principle behind &krusader; is based on the <ulink url="
"\"http://www.softpanorama.org/OFM/index.shtml\">Orthodox File Manager (OFM)</"
"ulink>, dual-pane filemanagers (<application>Midnight Commander</"
"application>, <trademark class=\"registered\">Norton Commander</trademark>, "
"&etc;), it is certain that &krusader; is able to handle all the standard "
"Copy, Move, Delete, &etc; file operations."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; Naloga projekta je ustvariti <quote>vse-v-enem</quote> "
"upravitelja datotek, ki bo delal vse običajne stvari, ki jih od njega "
"pričakujete, in še več. Ker je načelo &krusader; temelji na <ulink url="
"\"http://www.softpanorama.org/OFM/index.shtml\">ortodoksnem upravitelju "
"datotek (OFM)</ulink>, upravljalnikih datotek z dvojnim podoknom "
"(<application>Midnight Commander</application >, <trademark class="
"\"registered\">Norton Commander</trademark>, &etc;), je gotovo, da "
"&krusader; je sposoben obravnavati vse standardne funkcije kopiranja, "
"premikanja, brisanja &etc; operacije datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"From the start, virtual file systems became the main focus. <link linkend="
"\"vfs\">Virtual file systems (VFS)</link> are an abstracted layer over all "
"kinds of archived information (ZIP files, &FTP; servers, TAR archives, &NFS; "
"filesystems, SAMBA shares, ISO &CD;/&DVD; images, RPM catalogs, &etc;), "
"which allow the user to access all the information in these divergent types "
"of file systems transparently - just like entering an ordinary sub-folder. "
"Files can then be copied or moved around (except ISO, rpm, tar.gz) between "
"these data sources/containers effortlessly. &krusader; currently supports "
"VFSs for all popular and some specialized types of archives (ace, arj, "
"bzip2, gzip, iso, lha, rar, tar, zip and 7-zip), configuration packages "
"(rpm, deb), and traditional remote file system types (&FTP;, &NFS;, Samba, "
"FISH, SFTP)."
msgstr ""
"Že od samega začetka so postali glavni poudarek virtualni datotečni sistemi. "
"<link linkend=\"vfs\">Navidezni datotečni sistemi (VFS)</link> so "
"abstrahirana plast nad vsemi vrstami arhiviranih informacij (datoteke ZIP, "
"&FTP; strežniki, arhivi TAR, &NFS; datotečni sistemi, delitve SAMBA, ISO "
"&CD;/ slike &DVD;, katalogi RPM &etc;), ki uporabniku omogočajo pregleden "
"dostop do vseh informacij v teh različnih vrstah datotečnih sistemov - tako "
"kot bi vstopili v običajno podmapo. Datoteke je nato mogoče preprosto "
"kopirati ali premikati (razen ISO, rpm, tar.gz) med temi viri podatkov/"
"vsebniki. &krusader; trenutno podpira VFS za vse priljubljene in nekatere "
"specializirane vrste arhivov (ace, arj, bzip2, gzip, iso, lha, rar, tar, zip "
"in 7-zip), konfiguracijske pakete (rpm, deb) in tradicionalne vrste "
"oddaljenih datotečnih sistemov (&FTP;, &NFS;, Samba, FISH, SFTP)."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader; also includes a built-in Mount-Manager <link linkend=\"mount-man"
"\">MountMan</link>, which enables you to mount or unmount file systems of "
"all types with a click of a mouse. The user is able to obtain usage and "
"other property information easily, in a consistent and understandable format "
"in seconds. Ease and consistency is the goal."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; vključuje tudi vgrajen Mount-Manager <link linkend=\"mount-man"
"\">MountMan</link>, ki vam omogoča pripenjanje ali odpenjanje datotečnih "
"sistemov vseh vrst s klikom miške. Uporabnik lahko enostavno, v dosledni in "
"razumljivi obliki v nekaj sekundah pridobi podatke o uporabi in druge "
"lastnosti. Enostavnost in doslednost sta cilj."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <link linkend=\"bookman\">Bookmark-Manager</link> for local files/remote "
"&URL;s and an <link linkend=\"krusearcher\">Advanced Search module</link> is "
"also included to speed the locating of needed files. &krusader; also allows "
"the user to configure Toolbars in order to provide a wide variety of "
"additional functionality, such as File Comparison (several user selectable "
"methods available), Multiple File Rename, and standard Terminal windows."
msgstr ""
"Vključena sta tudi <link linkend=\"bookman\">upravitelj zaznamkov</link> za "
"lokalne datoteke/oddaljene &URL;-je in <link linkend=\"krusearcher\">modul "
"za napredno iskanje</link> za hitrejše iskanje potrebnih datoteke. "
"&krusader; prav tako omogoča uporabniku, da konfigurira orodne vrstice, da "
"zagotovi široko paleto dodatnih funkcij, kot je primerjava datotek (na voljo "
"je več uporabniško izbranih metod), preimenovanje več datotek in standardna "
"terminalska okna."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Advanced users benefit greatly from being able to carry out clerical tasks "
"effortlessly, without distraction from the real task at hand. Convenient "
"shortcut keys enable the user to navigate folder trees with ease, create "
"multiple tabbed folder views simultaneously, and access fully functional "
"history lists. Due to efficient programming and low system overhead, "
"&krusader; is perhaps the most responsive all around system management tool "
"used to access the full potential of a computer using &plasma;, or any other "
"standards compliant &X-Window; window manager. Although designed "
"specifically for - and tightly integrated with - &plasma;, &krusader; works "
"equally well with GNOME, MATE, Enlightenment, &windowmaker;, IceWM, XFCE, "
"&etc;, as long as the &kde-frameworks; libraries are installed."
msgstr ""
"Napredni uporabniki imajo veliko koristi od tega, da lahko brez težav "
"opravljajo pisarniška opravila, ne da bi se odvrnili od resničnega opravila. "
"Priročne tipke za bližnjice omogočajo uporabniku enostavno krmarjenje po "
"drevesih map, ustvarjanje več pogledov mape z zavihki hkrati in dostop do "
"popolnoma funkcionalnih seznamov zgodovine. Zaradi učinkovitega "
"programiranja in nizkih sistemskih stroškov je &krusader; je morda najbolj "
"odzivno orodje za upravljanje sistema, ki se uporablja za dostop do "
"celotnega potenciala računalnika z uporabo &plasma; ali katerega koli "
"drugega standarda, skladnega z &X-Window; upravitelj oken. Čeprav je "
"zasnovan posebej za &plasma; in je tesno povezan z njo, &krusader; deluje "
"enako dobro z GNOME, MATE, Enlightenment, &windowmaker;, IceWM, XFCE &etc;, "
"dokler &kde-frameworks; knjižnice so nameščene."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"New extensibility is provided by the flexible <link linkend=\"useractions"
"\">UserActions</link>, a &krusader; innovation that allows unlimited "
"additional custom functionality to be added to suit the specific needs of "
"users. We are planning to develop more modules in the near future, thereby "
"enhancing &krusader;. Information on what is proposed, approved, or remains "
"to be completed can be found in the <ulink url=\"https://invent.kde.org/"
"utilities/krusader\">&krusader; GitLab page</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Novo razširljivost zagotavljajo prilagodljiva <link linkend=\"useractions"
"\">uporabniška dejanja</link>, &krusader; inovacija, ki omogoča dodajanje "
"neomejenih dodatnih funkcij po meri, ki ustrezajo posebnim potrebam "
"uporabnikov. V bližnji prihodnosti nameravamo razviti več modulov in s tem "
"izboljšati &krusader;. Informacije o tem, kaj je predlagano, odobreno ali "
"kar je treba še dokončati, najdete v <ulink url=\"https://invent.kde.org/"
"utilities/krusader\">&krusader; Stran GitLab</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"No other program we know of, offers so many useful, easily accessible "
"features in such an intuitive and simple format. Best of all, we listen, and "
"implement good suggestions that are consonant with the &krusader; Project's "
"goal: making &krusader; the very best File Manager available."
msgstr ""
"Noben drug program, ki ga poznamo, ne ponuja toliko uporabnih, lahko "
"dostopnih funkcij v tako intuitivni in preprosti obliki. Najboljše od vsega "
"pa je, da poslušamo in izvajamo dobre predloge, ki so v skladu z &krusader; "
"Cilj projekta: izdelava &krusader; najboljši upravitelj datotek, ki je na "
"voljo."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "We hope you will enjoy it - we do!"
msgstr "Upamo, da boste uživali - mi uživamo!"
